Grid Layout:
- Columns 1-5: Project intro (icon, title, description, CTA)
- Columns 6-9: Metadata (team, category chips, role, timeline)
- Columns 10-12: Outcomes (bulleted list)

Separator Lines:
- Border-top: 1px solid rgba(234, 234, 237, 0.18)
- Spacing: py: 17px

Category Chips:
- Background: rgba(234, 234, 237, 0.18)
- Padding: 2px 8px
- Border radius: 8px
- Font: 16px Instrument Sans Medium
- Wrap: flex-wrap

Accessibility:
- Section: role="region", aria-label="[Project Name] overview"
- Button: Clear focus state, aria-label="View [Project] case study"
